deck: Scott Reichert co-founded Indigo Comics with his brother, Rob, and serves as a principle creator, contributor, and editor. In addition to comic book creating, Scott also plays guitar, sings, and is an avid Baltimore Orioles fan.
name: Scott Michael Reichert

description:
Shane Filer is the author of the novel Exit from Biblio Publishing, USA. Shane writes novels and comics, as well as directing television advertising and corporate videos. He lives in London.

He's written several issues of DC Thompson's Commando and ambitions include to write Wonder Woman for DC, and revive (properly this time) Dan Dare.

He likes oranges, orange juice, and orange furniture— in fact even the color orange. Why? Well, because it’s the best color, of course.
name: Shane Filer

deck: Artist known for his wood engraving work. His wordless novels have paved the way of graphic novels.
name: Lynd Ward
